<div class="status-header">
    <div class="tag">PAYMENT REQUIRED</div>
    <h1>Payment Instructions</h1>
    <p>Please fund the escrow account to proceed with Order #{{orderId}}</p>
</div>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Order Number</div>
        <div class="info-value">#{{orderId}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Total Amount</div>
        <div class="info-value">₹{{amount}}</div>
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Next Steps</h3>
<ol style="padding-left: 20px; color: #475569; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
    <li>Review the <strong>Proforma Invoice</strong> in your dashboard.</li>
    <li>Transfer the total amount to the BulkMandi Escrow account.</li>
    <li>Upload the <strong>UTR / Payment Reference</strong> in the order execution page.</li>
</ol>

<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
    <a href="{{ctaUrl}}" class="btn">View Payment Dashboard</a>
</div>
